name: Death Star Gunner
Lore: 'Most gunners in the Imperial Navy once aspired to be TIE pilots, but lacked sufficient skills to fly starfighters. A few were assigned to the Death Star to man the main artillery.',
Text: 'If on Death Star: Cumulatively adds 2 to total of Commence Primary Ignition. OR During your control phase, may send this gunner to your Used Pile and take Superlaser into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
